# Tell — always apply

Read USER_STORY.md: we build for **Priya** (solo founder, AI-built UI looks generic, demo tomorrow).

## Golden rules
1. Deterministic core — zero LLM in `packages/core`
2. Never auto-apply fixes — human applies in Cursor
3. Zod schemas at every boundary (`@tell/schema`)
4. Tokens only in `apps/web` — no raw hex in classNames
5. Product = capture → diagnose → art-direct → reconcile loop (not a dashboard)

